properties.description:
The Caravan Park is situated in the Narrogin town site yet close to the nature-filled bushland of Foxes Lair, where many guests go for leisurely bush walks or mountain bike rides and to take in and enjoy the beautiful birdlife and wildflowers.

- Self-contained holiday units, powered and unpowered caravan and campsites;
- Our Caravan Park is dog friendly (Pets are not allowed in the Self Contained Holiday Units);
- Close to town and local arts & crafts centre, visitors centre, cafes, deli, post office, retail shopping, service stations, butcher, banks, hotels and 7 day a week grocery stores;
- EV Charging Station;
- Close to Narrogin Regional Leisure Centre with heated indoor pool, squash courts, gym and fitness classes;
Town water, laundry and campers' kitchen, with free BBQ's;
- Dump point access;
- Welcome to Caravan Clubs, grey nomads, families, couples and singles;
- Mobility equipment access-friendly;
- Free Wi-Fi;
- Caravan Park $10 gift voucher issued to patrons of van sites and accommodation units upon arrival (conditions apply).

This park is perfect for families, overnight stays and travellers of all ages. We hope you enjoy your holiday whether it be a short stay or a getaway. Narrogin Caravan Park is the ideal place for you to visit whilst exploring what our Wheatbelt town has to offer. Stop and take the time out to absorb the surroundings and the great atmosphere. 

Come stay, relax and enjoy!
